00:30:02,108 --> 00:30:02,210
Yeah?

288
00:30:02,230 --> 00:30:02,789
You're going for lunch?

289
00:30:03,142 --> 00:30:08,027
And at lunch, just to remind you, it'll be a formal lunch.

